Uses of Package
is.merkor.core

Packages that use is.merkor.core
is.merkor.core A package containing the core data and dictionary interfaces for access to MerkOr data. 
is.merkor.core.redis.data Implementations of data classes for the access of MerkOr data stored on a Redis server. 
is.merkor.core.redis.dictionaries Contains implementations of dictionaries and parsers to access MerkOr data from a Redis server
